# Errors
#
ENoKeys:FATAL: Couldn't open settings file.
ENoConfig:FATAL: Couldn't open config file and Zap not loaded or is broken. You're in trouble.
ENoMenus:FATAL: Couldn't open menus file.
ENoExternal:FATAL: Couldn't open external file.
ENoRun:FATAL: Couldn't open the ZapUser !ZapRun file.
ENoBoot:FATAL: Couldn't open the ZapUser !ZapBoot file.
ENoTemplate:FATAL: Templates file missing or corrupt.
EBadInternals:FATAL: Couldn't access internal files.
EBadOutput:Couldn't save changes.
EBadConfig:Suspicious !Config file format: potential for data loss!
ELongConfig:Suspicious !Config file format: is !Zap more recent than !ZapConfig?
ETooManyPaths:You cannot specify more than 256 path checks.
ETooManyZapPaths:There are more than 256 path checks specified; some will be lost. Please contact the author of ZapConfig.
ETooManyKeymaps:You can only have 255 alternate keymaps.
EBadRunTemplates:Template set badly defined in the ZapUser !ZapRun file: resetting to 'Default'.
EBadTemplates:Can't find Zap's templates directory, or directory is empty.
ENoSuchMode:This mode doesn't have an entry in the !Config file. To edit it, load the mode in Zap and choose Save options, then rerun ZapConfig.
ETextModeVital:You can't delete Text mode's options. If you have problems, try Sanitise.
ETemplMenu:Couldn't create templates menu, probably because ZapTemplates$Path is too long.
